d News Nigeria. The National Emergency Management Agency (NEMA) on Sunday, visited victims of Saturday’s flooding in Gwagwalada Area Council in the Federal Capital Territory (FCT) Abuja. The visit was to ascertain the level of destruction caused by the flood that submerged more than 50 buildings in the territory. The flood from a… July 27, 2020 In "News" This year‘s rainy season has brought tears and sorrows for many communities in the northern part of the country as they were ravaged by flood which accompanied the rains. September 8, 2018 In "News" This year‘s rainy season has brought tears and sorrows for many communities in the northern part of the country as they were ravaged by flood which accompanied the rains. September 8, 2018 In "News"